<!--
  LIVE SCENE CUSTOM PLAY SNIPPET

  Adds SOUL rolling to the Play menu on the live scene page.

  FILE: ares-webportal/app/components/live-scene-custom-play.hbs

  CONFIRMED EXTENSION POINT:
  AresMUSH's LiveSceneControl invokes LiveSceneCustomPlay inside the Play
  dropdown and passes it the current scene and custom scene data. The
  standard live-scene-custom-play.hbs file is empty and intended for game
  additions like this one.

  INSTALLATION:

  1. Open the file named above in your ares-webportal checkout.
  2. Paste the component invocation below into it.
  3. Also install custom-install/custom_scene_data.snippet.rb in the game
     server checkout. Its flags control whether the GM review entry appears.
  4. Rebuild and deploy the web portal.

  The component displays results privately. It never adds a roll result to
  the scene transcript.
-->

{{soul/roll scene=this.scene custom=this.custom}}
